title: "log lines 'Injecting 1 queued message' and 'Queued inbound message for busy session' should have the session at the start like other log lines, eg: \n[07:52:33.472] INFO  [telegram:58495225:58495225] LLM native stream dispatch provider=openai-codex model=gpt-5.4 msgs=82\n[07:52:47.291] INFO  [telegram:58495225:58495225] Cost: model=gpt-5.4 prompt=61696 completion=535 cost=.000000 session_total=.0000"
